          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The content of a Live Activity may become out of date before you can update it. For example, a person",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "may be in an area without a network connection, causing the Live Activity to not receive updates.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "To tell people that they are looking at outdated Live Activity content, you can configure",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ActivityKit/documentation/ActivityKit/ActivityContent/staleDate",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for your Live Activity. At the specified",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "date, the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ActivityKit/documentation/ActivityKit/Activity/activityState",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " changes to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "stale",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and you can",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "update the Live Activity to indicate that its content is out of date.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
